<paragraph id="8BB0595AFF92FFD8ECDE4253B76DF91E" blockId="8.[151,1436,1494,1735]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8ECDE4253B578F9EF" bold="true" box="[199,315,1566,1591]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C0F22D9FF92FFD8ED5E4252B669F9EF" authority="Kirby, 1892" authorityName="Kirby" authorityYear="1892" box="[327,554,1566,1591]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Teucer" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8ED5E4252B5CCF9EE" box="[327,399,1567,1590]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Teucer</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E24ABFF92FFD8ED864253B669F9EF" author="Kirby" box="[415,554,1566,1591]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" refString="Kirby, W. F. (1892) A synonymic catalogue of Lepidoptera-Heterocera. Gurney &amp; Jackson, London, 951 pp." type="book" year="1892">
Kirby, 
<number id="3DC74B7DFF92FFD8EDEB4252B669F9EF" box="[498,554,1567,1591]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" value="1892.0">1892</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is an unnecessary replacement name for 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F22D9FF92FFD8E8074253B176F9EF" authority="Felder, 1874" authorityName="Felder" authorityYear="1874" box="[1054,1333,1566,1591]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Telioneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8E8074253B0D7F9EF" box="[1054,1172,1566,1591]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Telioneura</emphasis>
Felder, 
<number id="3DC74B7DFF92FFD8E8E44252B176F9EF" box="[1277,1333,1567,1591]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" value="1874.0">1874</number>
</taxonomicName>
(erected because of 
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8ED3A420FB5EBF983" box="[291,424,1602,1627]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Telejoneura</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E24ABFF92FFD8EDAF420FB627F983" author="Rondani" box="[438,612,1602,1627]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" refString="Rondani, C. (1864) Dipterorum species et genera aliqua exotica revisa et annotata novis nonullis descriptis. Archivio de la Zoologia, l'Anatomia e la Fisiologia, 3 (1), 1 - 99 + 1 pl." type="journal article" year="1864">
Rondani, 
<number id="3DC74B7DFF92FFD8EE33420FB627F983" box="[554,612,1602,1627]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" value="1864.0">1864</number>
</bibRefCitation>
, Diptera). Therefore, the valid combination for this name would be 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F22D9FF92FFD8EC8E422BB5D3F9A7" box="[151,400,1638,1663]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Telioneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="imbecillus">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8EC8E422BB5D3F9A7" box="[151,400,1638,1663]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Telioneura imbecillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, as mentioned in the original description, this species is indeed close to 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F22D9FF92FFD8E99E422AB5E9F97B" authority="Druce, 1883" authorityName="Druce" authorityYear="1883" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Telioneura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carmania">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8E99E422AB540F97B" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">T. carmania</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E24ABFF92FFD8ED0842C6B5E2F97B" author="Druce" box="[273,417,1675,1699]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" refString="Druce, H. (1883) Descriptions of new species of Zygaenidae and Arctiidae. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London, no volume assigned, 372 - 384." type="proceedings paper" year="1883">
Druce, 
<number id="3DC74B7DFF92FFD8ED7F42C6B5E2F97B" box="[358,417,1675,1699]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" value="1883.0">1883</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, which was recently transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F22D9FF92FFD8EF2E42C7B020F97B" authority="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" box="[823,1123,1674,1699]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Ecdemus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8EF2E42C7B7DFF97B" box="[823,924,1674,1699]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Ecdemus</emphasis>
Herrich-Schäffer
</taxonomicName>
, [
<number id="3DC74B7DFF92FFD8E86F42C7B0F0F97B" box="[1142,1203,1674,1699]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" value="1855.0">1855</number>
] (
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E24ABFF92FFD8E8D042C7B497F91F" author="Pinheiro" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" refString="Pinheiro, L. R. &amp; Duarte, M. (2013) Taxonomic notes on Ctenuchina, Euchromiina, and Phaegopterina (Lepidoptera, Erebidae, Arctiinae, Arctiini). Florida Entomologist, 96 (2), 351 - 359. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1653 / 024.096.0255" type="journal article" year="2013">
Pinheiro &amp; Duarte 
<number id="3DC74B7DFF92FFD8EC8E42E2B497F91F" box="[151,212,1711,1735]" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" value="2013.0">2013</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). Hence the transfer of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F22D9FF92FFD8EDC042E2B6DDF91F" box="[473,670,1710,1735]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Teucer" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="imbecillus">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8EDC042E2B6DDF91F" box="[473,670,1710,1735]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Teucer imbecillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F22D9FF92FFD8EEDB42E3B764F91F" box="[706,807,1710,1735]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Ecdemus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97B8548FF92FFD8EEDB42E3B764F91F" box="[706,807,1710,1735]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="513">Ecdemus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
